The '''Esselian New Order Party''' was a political party on [[Esseles/Legends|Esseles]] during the time of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. Led by [[Jamson Freller]], it advocated the philosophy of [[Humanocentrism]] as well as complete allegiance to the Empire. Freller questioned the ability of [[Esselian Hall|Hall]] [[President/Legends|President]] [[Cambira Ralle]] to lead the planet during a series of nonhuman workers' strikes.

The New Order Party was often allied with the [[Cardean Party]], and opposed to the [[Forad Party]] within the Esselian Hall.

Following the [[Esselian Hall election, 2 ABY|election]] of [[2 ABY/Legends|2 ABY]], the Esselian New Order Party won the majority.<ref name="GNN8">{{JournalCite|8|Galaxywide NewsNets}}</ref>

